node.text:
Rick Perry and Marcus Luttrell on the porch filming a video talking about why we are FOR Jake Ellzey for Congress. 

With lots of false, negative attacks flying around from DC special interests, it’s important to say who you SUPPORT and why you SUPPORT them!  We support Jake Ellzey for Congress.

node.text: Homeownership changed my life. Benchmark Mortgage has championed Veterans and first responders for 20 years and will always provide a first-class mortgage experience. We teamed up with Benchmark to bring you this year’s Patriot Tour and are proud to stand by their NEVER QUIT attitude toward serving our veterans and first responders.

node.title: The American Dream for Our American Heroes

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Marcus Luttrell on July 09, 2021 tagging @dairylandmotorcycle. May be an image of 1 person, motorcycle, outdoors and text that says 'MOTORCYCLE DAY AY OF GOOD'.

node.text: The rain didn’t stop us from giving back on this #nationalmotorcycleday with @dairylandmotorcycle. The crew and I had a great time giving back to the #Veteran and #FirstResponder community today at @houstonvamc and Houston Fire Department #8. These well deserving people should always be taken care of and any chance we get to do that is a good day! I challenge you to get out there and do some good in your community. 🇺🇸 #ad

node.text: 16 years has gone by, but it never gets easy. The boys are missed every day especially today, but today they got to meet my best friend. Mr. Rigby has been there for me since the day we met and I’ve enjoyed every minute with him. He was by my side when I met my wife, when we got married, when we had the kids and every milestone ever since. June 28th will double down as the toughest day of my life. May God Bless you and welcome you into Heaven Mr. Rigby. I will miss you.

node.text:
Rick Perry and Marcus Luttrell on the porch filming a video talking about why we are FOR Jake Ellzey for Congress. 

With lots of false, negative attacks flying around from DC special interests, it’s important to say who you SUPPORT and why you SUPPORT them!  We support Jake Ellzey for Congress.
